{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act42side", "eventName": "眾生行記", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "MT-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "共融", "storyInfo": "牧首邀請安多恩參與育嬰聖堂未來更宏大的計劃。能天使因試圖阻礙降生儀式被逮捕，所有非薩科塔都被銃騎以各種理由帶走。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g2_baptismlobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_comfortbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "木攀獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個響動……別緊張，孩子。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧首。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#16$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#16$2"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保育員先生，你也在。真是辛苦了，感謝你在這段時間的付出。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#16$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是盡我所能。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#16$2"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個小傢伙還很脆弱。安多恩，帶牠回到牠的母親身邊吧。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我隨後便去找你們。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#16$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧首，您看起來有點虛弱……需要我護送您回去嗎？", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無妨，只是剛剛的心跳聲仍在我的體內迴響。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不只那位母親，帕特里奇昂，我聽到了不計其數的心跳在共鳴，幾乎快震塌這座聖堂。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論出身，不論種族，人們已經開始連結……但也有人已經拒絕了我們所展示的未來。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "降生儀式可以到此為止了，不必讓同胞們在此逗留，準備下一步的工作吧。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了。還請您去休息，這邊剩下的事情交給我就好。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g2_baptismlobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "bse"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "soundvolume", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再次感謝各位來到育嬰聖堂。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論諸位是否理解，又怎樣看待先前牧首在峰會上提出的主張，這隻木攀獸的降生與啟聖，無疑都給予了我們更明晰的啟示。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於如何跨越“國家”、“種族”的隔閡，關於如何從根本上消弭仇恨、締造和平……關於如何共同應對懸於頭頂的災異。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以降生儀式為起點，第二屆萬國峰會將正式進入下一階段——", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭將向所有薩科塔之外的種族分享光環！", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“願主將屬靈的恩典賜予每一人。”", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g1_nurserytemplesquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}},