"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（試圖抓頭）", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_213_mostma_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安，怎麼回事？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#12$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……一兩句話說不清楚。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不然，我幫你爭取兩分鐘的逃跑時間？", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#7$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "能天使", "content": "也可以——"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "能天使", "end": "true", "content": "還是別給我老姐惹麻煩了，下次吧！", "joined": "也可以——還是別給我老姐惹麻煩了，下次吧！"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我是不是打擾你們幾位好友團聚了？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安樞機，你自己一個人就能夠將嫌犯帶回第七廳嗎？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，需要支援……？畢竟試圖破壞育嬰聖堂、干涉萬國峰會，可是關係重大！", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#3$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不放心的話，前輩你可以和我一起，或者讓銃騎監督。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼說話嘛。畢竟根據阿摩斯輔佐官的證詞，你確實之前就在其他案發現場發現了蕾繆樂的蹤跡……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#3$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#5$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是想說，我試圖包庇自己的妹妹？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#5$2"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並非如此，畢竟都是間接證據，不足以說明你採取了什麼行動。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還記得我們之前在聖堂內的談話嗎？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很欣賞你的能力和辦事手段，“噤聲的蕾繆安”，不過我也清楚你那些美好的特質一般在什麼時候最能體現出來……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#9$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況這次牽涉到的是你的妹妹，我們有所懷疑也是在所難免，請你理解。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#9$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你們大可放心。放小樂背著一身罪名亂跑，並不能真正幫到她。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯嗯，只要蕾繆樂能夠配合，我相信這裡面的誤會一定能解開的。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍微等等，“微光守夜人”，還有……萬國信使莫斯提馬。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位請暫時留在育嬰聖堂，教皇廳有些任務需要交給兩位。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g1_nurserytemplesquare", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1779_1#4$2", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小樂姐……被帶走了？", "name": "梵里妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1779_1#4$2"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚，好不容易說服老師讓我出來，結果還是來不及……", "name": "梵里妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1779_1#4$2"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這，怎麼辦，梵妮，你還能做些什麼？", "name": "梵里妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1779_1#4$2"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g4_nurseryindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必叩門，安多恩。我沒有任何事需要迴避你。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子的母親？", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經入睡了。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我把這孩子帶了過來。牠的羽毛還沒長齊，但驚人地有活力。我猜，您或許會想再摸摸牠。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#11$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。這對我來說也是一種慰藉。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡……", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還記得嗎？你我來到拉特蘭後，為了安置這孩子的母親，臨時建了這間屋子，後來這裡成為了整座聖堂的第一間育嬰室。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。我和您一起鋪好了這簡陋卻溫暖的床鋪，掛好了安撫鈴，讓牠得以安睡。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然這個房間早已不再使用，但我時常會重回這裡，哪怕只是簡單地禱告。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這裡是你我的起點。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（愜意地舒展身體）", "name": "木攀獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1790_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能感受到，牠也喜歡這裡。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，這孩子的光環真閃亮啊。你抱牠進來的時候，我就感受到了。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是您一直以來堅信的奇蹟，牧首。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我仍不明白，您是如何在最初見到牠的母親時，就看到了奇蹟的預兆？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，安多恩，我那時沒有看到任何預兆，我只看到你的內心在掙扎。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠那時已油盡燈枯，需要的並非救治，而是安葬。但你仍想救牠，你不希望這個念頭在常識的沖刷下消散。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我堅信的，是你精心保護的那一個念頭，可以締造生命的奇蹟。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生命是偉大的，“常識”這種尺規從來都無法用來測量它的歷程。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任何人都會有救牠的念頭，牧首。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以任何人都可以締造奇蹟。或許就是因為人們不願相信信仰的力量，奇蹟才會被稱作奇蹟。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩，你難道不曾想過，是光環賦予了薩科塔信仰，還是信仰為薩科塔帶來了光環？", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的律法、共感和銃武以及我們依託這些建立起的樂園……", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們的開端，難道真如常識所示，只是一種毫無來由的恩賜？", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我不知道，牧首。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過去有其開端，未來亦然。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "育嬰聖堂……這座高聳入雲的巨型結構，並非於一日之內落成。它的開端也只是這樣一間平平無奇的育嬰室。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的育嬰室……", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你我最初可曾手握宏偉聖堂的藍圖？不，我們只是想要一個安全而舒適的房間，用來安置那位母親……", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它依然一發不可收拾地演化成了現在的樣子。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，一個所有人都得救的未來，當然可以起始於你我的信仰。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧首……我追隨您，是因為我為了那樣一個未來苦尋已久，而您恰巧知曉道路。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不曾想過，也無法理解，為何您會認為那條道路的開端在於我。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#2$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我終究只能做些微不足道的小事。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1800_1#3$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "微不足道的小事，驚天動地的壯舉，不過一線之隔，一念之差。你苦尋多年才跋涉至此，不應該為了這種無謂的區別而止步。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，除了照顧好這對母子，我需要你打起精神，去做更多的事情……比如，下一場降生儀式。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g12_firearmsworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們來得比通知時間還早啊。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#2$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該收拾的都已經收拾完了，你們直接貼上封條吧，貼完我就能回去睡覺了。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#2$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕特里奇昂？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#2$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，差點罵錯人了。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是說最後的接收步驟是公證所負責嗎？怎麼來的是銃騎？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前提是，一切正常，你沒有做什麼手腳。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛檢查了工坊內的材料室以及所有的操作設備，明顯有近期使用過的跡象。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，阿摩斯樞機輔佐官上次來的時候應該聲明過——", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簽署工坊關閉文件後，銃械工坊一應業務即告終止，私下進行任何守護銃或爆破物相關的製作活動將被視為違背條律。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我盤下這間小工坊也有幾十年了，說關就關，我捨不得……", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後這點時間，忍不住讓這些老朋友再動一下，聽聽聲響，流流眼淚，有什麼問題嗎？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "類似的說辭，您已經說過一遍了。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的學徒，梵里妮小姐，您在育嬰聖堂門口帶走了她——她人呢？", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能又溜回去看降生儀式了吧。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不是小孩子了，我的視力又不好，怎麼管得了！", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，潘格尼尼先生，讓我們換個地方說吧。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我不願意呢？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如非必要，我不應該對您採取任何強制性的手段。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是帕特里奇昂那傢伙讓你來的，對吧？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……請吧。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g6_laterano_chapelin", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銃騎閣下，您找席德佳？", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不在修道院裡嗎？", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在、她在的……但她剛好出了點意外，還在休息。", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，這要從哪裡開始說起呢……", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天，突然有一輛告解車停在修道院門口，席德佳修女就躺在車廂裡……不、不省人事。", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告解車被設定好了終點，現場也沒有其他人在，我們不清楚她到底遭遇了什麼。", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銃騎閣下，或許可以等她醒來，我們再讓她去找您。", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事態緊急，帶我去見她。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳……請不要為難格蘭修女。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "席德佳，你醒了，感覺還好嗎？桌上的……", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心放心，只是有點暈而已。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經喝過桌上的熱粥了，咳是因為剛剛燙到了。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#1$1"}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銃騎閣下，您是為阿爾圖羅小姐的事情來的吧？", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#11$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您聽我說，阿爾圖羅小姐她確實擅自離開了蘭登修道院……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我已經在發現後的第一時間出去追了，請相信我，我已經找到她了！但……發生了一些意想不到的事情……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請再給蘭登修道院一點時間，不，請再給我一點時間。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "席德佳修女，你介意跟我們走一趟嗎？", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好，我跟您去。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，這位修女，你也一起吧。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我？", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蘭修女和這件事情沒有關係。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅小姐的監管事宜一直是我在負責，是我的失職……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別緊張，席德佳修女。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蘭登修道院發生了這麼重大的事情，教皇廳需要知曉所有細節，盡可能收集相關線索。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，請跟我們走吧。", "name": "銃騎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_358_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}